CustomField.description: This field is optional. It is populated by a user or a data integration. The GIIN of the disregarded entity account holder. (Global Intermediary Identification Number, a 19-digit number assigned to certain entities and used by a financial institution to identify itself to withholding agents and tax administrations for FATCA reporting.)
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The GIIN of the disregarded entity account holder. (Global Intermediary Identification Number.)
CustomField.label: GIIN
